title: Low-Carb Sausage And Egg Breakfast Cups
directions: .Mix sausage, salt, pepper, garlic powder, onion powder, and paprika in a bowl until well combined.
Grease a muffin tin and start to form shells with the sausage mix. Cover the sides and leave room in the middle for the eggs.
In a separate bowl, mix the eggs, salt, and pepper.
Pour egg mixture into the middle of each cup.
Optional: top with shredded cheese, tomatoes, spinach, or toppings of your choice.
ingredients: 1 pound ground sausage (pork, chicken, or turkey)
